<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefe5bbaa-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6501"><num value="6501">§ 6501.</num><heading> Purposes</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">It is the purpose of this chapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefe5bbab-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6501/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> to establish national standards governing the marketing of certain agricultural products as organically produced products;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefe5bbac-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6501/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> to assure consumers that organically produced products meet a consistent standard; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefe5bbad-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6501/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> to facilitate interstate commerce in fresh and processed food that is organically produced.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idefe5bbae-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXXI/s2102">Pub. L. 101–624, title XXI, § 2102</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3935">104 Stat. 3935</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idefe5bbaf-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idefe5bbb0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitle" id="idefe5bbb1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXXI/s2101">Pub. L. 101–624, title XXI, § 2101</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3935">104 Stat. 3935</ref>, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/101/624/tXXI/s2101">“This title [enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘Organic Foods Production Act of 1990’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
